# Cursor Rules for Suja's Kitchen

## Component Usage
- ALWAYS use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/*` for all UI elements
- NEVER create custom components when a shadcn component exists
- NEVER use emojis in code, text, or UI elements
- Use shadcn Button, Card, Badge, Avatar, Input, Label, Textarea, Select, Dialog, etc.
- Prefer shadcn components over custom styled divs

## Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling
- Primary color: #c91432
- Use shadcn's built-in variants and styling props
- Maintain consistent spacing and typography

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Follow Next.js 16+ App Router patterns
- Use 'use client' directive for client components
- Keep components modular and reusable

## File Structure
- Components in `components/` directory
- UI components in `components/ui/` (shadcn)
- Custom components in `components/` (not in ui folder)

## Best Practices
- Use shadcn components with proper TypeScript types
- Implement proper accessibility (aria labels, semantic HTML)
- Optimize images with Next.js Image component
- Use proper error boundaries and loading states
